<BaseLayout title="Editorial and Safety Policy" description="How GameHelp India writes, reviews and updates independent online-game payment and safety guidance." canonicalPath="/editorial-policy/">
<main id="main"><article class="prose"><span class="kicker">Trust and review standards</span><h1>Editorial and safety policy</h1><p>Our pages are written for users facing payment, account and security problems. They must not be used as a cover for gambling promotion or unofficial customer support.</p><h2>Neutral language</h2><p>We distinguish verified facts from allegations and user reports. An app is not labelled a scam without reliable evidence. Brand-specific pages clearly state that we are independent.</p><h2>No hidden promotion</h2><p>GameHelp India does not publish real-money game referrals, deposit offers, APK downloads, bonus links or covert redirects. Search crawlers and users receive the same content.</p><h2>Safety rules</h2><ul><li>Never request OTP, UPI PIN, password, CVV or remote access.</li><li>Never ask users to send money to recover money.</li><li>Never impersonate an operator, bank or Government authority.</li><li>Prioritise official bank, payment and cybercrime channels.</li></ul><h2>Updates</h2><p>Pages display their review date. Material corrections should be documented and app-specific claims rechecked before republication.</p></article></main>
</BaseLayout>
